## OpenCode-specific

- **Agents**: `plan` runs Opus, `build` runs local MLX (Qwen3.6-27B), `review` runs Sonnet.
  Switch with `/agent <name>` in the TUI.
- **Permissions matter**: `.git/**`, `node_modules/**`, `.env*`, and `**/secrets/**` are
  edit-denied at the config level. `git push` and destructive bash commands prompt
  before running. Don't try to circumvent these — surface the need instead.
- **MCP**: configured in `mcp` block of opencode.json. None enabled by default.
- **Plugin events** (for reference, when adding new plugins): `session.created`,
  `session.idle`, `tool.execute.before`/`.after`, `file.edited`, `permission.asked`.
  Plugins live in `~/.config/opencode/plugin/*.ts` (Bun-executed; `$` is Bun shell).
